Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.92,0:00:08.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这女人杀了我的女儿 杀了我女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.88,0:00:11.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去猎杀尸鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:19.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.90,0:00:24.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里肯定是他们的藏身之处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.83,0:00:26.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏夫 快看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.94,0:00:30.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.29,0:00:32.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以打开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.27,0:00:38.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大冢制材家的儿子
